      "content": "small steps don't really help when the hole just keeps getting bigger. i feel like i'm just dragging myself through every day and it's so exhausting. honestly, sometimes i look at the silence and i think... maybe the only way to actually get some peace and stop this weight is to just not be here anymore. it feels like the only way to make the hurting stop.",
